I bought this blanket for my daughter. It came packaged and an airtight bag with a beautiful ribbon wrapped around it. The blanket is beautiful fluffy and soft it looks exactly like the advertising picture. I always wash every single blanket linen and closed before use so this blanket was no different. It came in an airtight package with a pretty ribbon wrapped around it. When I opened the airtight bag it fluffed right up and there was a very strong smell to it. So straight to the washing machine it went tumble-dried it before I gave it to my daughter. She absolutely loves it!! I will buy again
